text: The Netherlands Antilles competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics in Rome, Italy. The nation returned to the Olympic Games after boycotting the 1956 Summer Olympics, joining the Netherlands in protest of the Soviet Union's invasion of Hungary. ==References== *Official Olympic Reports Category:Nations at the 1960 Summer Olympics 1960 Category:1960 in the Netherlands Antilles
title: Netherlands Antilles at the 1960 Summer Olympics
